STATE EX REL. HIGGINS
v.
MCCARTY 2019-0066 Supreme Court of Ohio. April 10, 2019

O'CONNOR, C.J., and KENNEDY, FRENCH, FISCHER, DEWINE, DONNELLY, and STEWART, JJ., concur.

MERIT DECISION WITHOUT OPINION

On respondent's motion for judgment on the pleadings. Motion granted. Cause dismissed.
